ss=\"CS_Layout_TR\"><td class=\"CS_Layout_TD\" id=\"cs_idCell2x1x1\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_1906907\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<p>The following river concessioners provide trips through Grand Canyon, Lees Ferry to Diamond Creek (226 river miles/364 km). Each company offers a variety of trips lasting 3 - 18 days in large motorized rafts, oared rafts, paddle rafts, and dories. Contact each company for more details.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.riveradventures.com/\" id=\"http://www.riveradventures.com/|\">Aramark-Wilderness River Adventures<br/>\nwww.riveradventures.com</a><br/>\nP.O. Box 717, Page, AZ 86040<br/>\n(800) 992-8022; (928) 645-3296; FAX (928) 645-6113</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.azraft.com/\" id=\"http://www.azraft.com/|\">Arizona Raft Adventures, LLC<br/>\nwww.azraft.com</a><br/>\n4050 East Huntington Drive, Flagstaff, AZ 86004<br/>\n(800) 786-7238; (928) 526-8200; FAX (928) 526-8246</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.raftarizona.com/\" id=\"http://www.raftarizona.com/|\">Arizona River Runners, Inc.<br/>\nwww.raftarizona.com</a><br/>\nP.O. Box 47788, Phoenix, AZ 85068-7788<br/>\n(800) 477-7238; (602) 867-4866; FAX (602) 867-2174</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.canyonexplorations.com/\" id=\"http://www.canyonexplorations.com/|\">Canyon Explorations/Canyon Expeditions<br/>\nwww.canyonexplorations.com</a><br/>\nP.O. Box 310, Flagstaff, AZ 86002<br/>\n(800) 654-0723; (928) 774-4559; FAX (928) 774-4655</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.canyoneers.com/\" id=\"http://www.canyoneers.com/|\">Canyoneers, Inc.<br/>\nwww.canyoneers.com</a><br/>\nP.O. Box 2997, Flagstaff, AZ 86003<br/>\n(800) 525-0924; (928) 526-0924; FAX (928) 527-9398</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.crateinc.com/\" id=\"http://www.crateinc.com/|\">Colorado River &amp; Trail Expeditions, Inc.<br/>\nwww.crateinc.com</a><br/>\nP.O. Box 57575, Salt Lake City, UT 84157-0575<br/>\n(800) 253-7328; (801) 261-1789; FAX (801) 268-1193</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.grandcanyondiscovery.com/\" id=\"http://www.grandcanyondiscovery.com/|\">Grand Canyon Discovery, LLC<br/>\nwww.grandcanyondiscovery.com</a><br/>\n4050 East Huntington Drive, Flagstaff, AZ 86004<br/>\n(800) 786-7238; (928) 526-8200; FAX (928) 526-8246</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.gcex.com/\" id=\"http://www.gcex.com/|\">Grand Canyon Expeditions Company<br/>\nwww.gcex.com</a><br/>\nP.O. Box 0, Kanab, UT 84741<br/>\n(800) 544-2691; (435) 644-2691</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.azraft.com/\" id=\"http://www.azraft.com/|\">Grand Canyon Raft Adventures<br/>\nwww.azraft.com</a><br/>\n4050 East Huntington Drive, Flagstaff, AZ 86004<br/>\n(800) 786-RAFT; (928) 526-8200; FAX (928) 526-8246</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.grandcanyonwhitewater.com/\" id=\"http://www.grandcanyonwhitewater.com/|\">Grand Canyon Whitewater, LLC<br/>\nwww.grandcanyonwhitewater.com</a><br/>\nPO Box 2848, Flagstaff, AZ 86003<br/>\n(800) 343-3121; (928) 779-2979; FAX (928) 779-2973</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.hatchriverexpeditions.com/\" id=\"http://www.hatchriverexpeditions.com/|\">Hatch River Expeditions, Inc.<br/>\nwww.hatchriverexpeditions.com</a><br/>\n5348 East Burris Lane, Flagstaff, AZ 86004<br/>\n(800) 856-8966; (928) 526-4700; FAX: (928) 526-4703</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.oars.com/\" id=\"http://www.oars.com/|\">O.A.R.S. Grand Canyon, Inc.<br/>\nwww.oars.com</a><br/>\nP.O. Box 67, Angles Camp, CA 95222,<br/>\n(800) 346-6277; (209) 736-2924; FAX (209) 736-2902</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.outdoorsunlimited.com/\" id=\"http://www.outdoorsunlimited.com/|\">Outdoors Unlimited<br/>\nwww.outdoorsunlimited.com</a><br/>\n6900 Townsend Winona Road, Flagstaff, AZ 86004<br/>\n(800) 637-7238; (928) 526-4546; FAX (928) 526-6185</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.twriver.com/\" id=\"http://www.twriver.com/|\">Tour West, Inc.<br/>\nwww.twriver.com</a><br/>\nP.O. Box 333, Orem, UT 84059<br/>\n(800) 453-9107; (801) 225-0755; FAX (801) 225-7979</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.westernriver.com/\" id=\"http://www.westernriver.com/|\">Western River Expeditions, Inc.<br/>\nwww.westernriver.com</a><br/>\n7258 Racquet Club Drive, Salt Lake City, UT 84121<br/>\n(800) 453-7450; (801) 942-6669; FAX (801) 942-8514</p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_5113384\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_5113384\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<p><span class=\"subheading\">Additional river info can be found at the following webpages.</span></p>\n<div class=\"table-wrapper\"><table cellpadding=\"2\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"\" summary=\"table containing links for river trip information\" width=\"100%\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"\" valign=\"top\"><strong>Commercial River Trips (River Concessioners)</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/one-day-river-trip.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1906934,one-day-river-trip.htm,11006|\">1 Day River Trips</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/river-concessioners.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1906904,river-concessioners.htm,11006|\">3-18 Day River Trips</a></li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n<td style=\"\" valign=\"top\"><strong>Noncommercial (Private) River Trips</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/overview-diamond-ck.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1932929,overview-diamond-ck.htm,11006|\">2-5 Day River Trips</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/overview-lees-ferry-diamond-ck.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1931507,overview-lees-ferry-diamond-ck.htm,11006|\">12-25 Day River Trips</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/river-faq.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1937558,river-faq.htm,11006|\">River FAQs</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/river_support.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1937759,river_support.htm,11006|\">River Trip Support Companies</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/weightedlottery.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1932935,weightedlottery.htm,11006|\">Weighted Lottery</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/noncommercial-riv-docs.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=2102042,noncommercial-riv-docs.htm,11006|\">Helpful Links</a></li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div>\n</div></div>\n</td></tr>\n</table></div>\n</div><!-- col-sm-12 -->\n</div><!-- row -->\n</div><!-- ColumnMain col-sm-9 -->\n</div><!-- ColumnGrid row -->\n</div><!-- end container -->\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 text-content-size text-content-style\">\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\">Last updated: March 12, 2025</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n <!-- ParkFooter -->\n<!--googleon: index-->\n\n</div><!-- end of <div main> -->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!-- the rest of the scripts are leftovers from before the centennial down and should be pared down where possible -->\n\n<link href=\"/common/commonspot/templates/assets/libs/colorbox/colorbox.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n\n<div class=\"modal fade\" id=\"outdated-browser\" role=\"dialog\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n</div>\n</body>",
